'''迈克尔·埃弗里特·卡普阿諾'''（{{lang-en|'''Michael Everett Capuano'''}}，{{bd|1952年|1月9日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物<ref name="rita-2010">{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/obituaries/articles/2010/07/21/rita_capuano_campaigned_with_vigor_for_husband_son_at_90/|author=Emma Stickgold|title=Rita Capuano; campaigned with vigor for husband, son; at 90|publisher=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]|date=July 21, 2010|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2013-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105223730/http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/obituaries/articles/2010/07/21/rita_capuano_campaigned_with_vigor_for_husband_son_at_90/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="post-bio">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/elections/2004/candidates/22079/|title=Biography: Michael Everett Capuano (D)|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213857/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/elections/2004/candidates/22079/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自2013年開始，他是{{link-en|麻薩諸塞州第七國會選區|Massachusetts's 7th congressional district}}選出的[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院議員]]。他的黨籍是[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]。在成為國會議員之前，卡普阿諾曾經擔任薩默維爾市的市長。

== 個人生活 ==
卡普阿諾的首名和中间名来自于祖父以及外祖父的名字，他有七個兄弟姐妹，其中一個死於分娩，另有一個在5歲時死於[[脊髓灰質炎|脊髓灰質炎]]。<ref name="rita-2010" />卡普阿諾在1974年與Barbara Teebagy結婚，他們有兩個兒子Michael和Joseph。<ref name="directory-2009">{{cite book|last1=Alston|first1=Farnsworth|last2=Carter|first2=Mary Ann|last3=Randolph|first3=Sarah (eds.)|year=2009|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9nL2Bhq3UYIC&pg=PA130|chapter=Michael E. Capuano|title=''Congressional Directory for the 111th Congress (2009–2010)''|location=Washington, D.C.|publisher=United States Government Publishing Office|pages=127–128|isbn=978-0-16-083727-2|access-date=2017-04-06|archive-date=2016-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401150929/https://books.google.com/books?id=9nL2Bhq3UYIC&pg=PA130|dead-url=no}}</ref>他是《[[神奇4俠_(2005年電影)|神奇4俠]]》和《[[美國隊長：復仇者先鋒|美國隊長：復仇者先鋒]]》電影系列演員[[基斯·伊雲斯|基斯·伊雲斯]]，以及肥皂劇《''{{link-en|One Life to Live|One Life to Live}}''》的[[史葛·伊雲斯|史葛·伊雲斯]]的舅舅。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.boston.com/culture/entertainment/2016/04/06/chris-evans-says-he-might-want-to-get-into-politics-someday |title = Chris Evans says he might want to get into politics someday |author = Kevin Slane |date = 2016-04-06 |publisher = boston.com |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-06 |archive-date = 2017-04-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170407054413/https://www.boston.com/culture/entertainment/2016/04/06/chris-evans-says-he-might-want-to-get-into-politics-someday |dead-url = no }}</ref>2003年，薩默維爾市為卡普阿諾創辦了一所新學校；米高·E·卡普阿諾幼兒中心（Michael E. Capuano Early Childhood Center）於當年9月正式開幕。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://capuano.house.gov/news/2003/pr090203.shtml |title = City of Somerville Names Early Childhood Center in Honor of Congressman Capuano |publisher = http://capuano.house.gov |language = en |access-date = 2017-04-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170117014229/https://capuano.house.gov/news/2003/pr090203.shtml |archive-date = 2017-01-17 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>

